{"tid":1844024,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"廣州民眾熱烈要求封城　廣州：不會封城","createTime":"2020-01-26T12:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T01:03:18.000Z","uid":76591,"like":215,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8e512b3fefc70c7d0ac5752919f85dc5a79cc7","tid":1844024,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"根據廣州市防控新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎疫情工作領導小組最新消息，自廣東啟動重大突發公共衛生事件一級響應以來，廣州市對確診病例、疑似病例和密切接觸者均按醫學隔離標準和診療規範實施隔離管控。為防止疫情擴散，特別是減少輸入性病例，在機場、車站、碼頭等場所採取了體溫監測措施，但不存在&ldquo; 封城 &rdquo;等說法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uBpFc6h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBpFc6h.png&h=e57caa73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/foUYKcY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfoUYKcY.png&h=9b491054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvQJaTT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvQJaTT.png&h=131c2358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34966845e97e93df312ff8f5a8a7cfcae8b2b62","tid":1844024,"uid":134202,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:37:44.000Z","msg":"信政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c657be3f1907cd038163ccc2cc583ca8e878b087","tid":1844024,"uid":52230,"like":355,"dislike":1,"score":354,"citedBy":18,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oak5pfw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foak5pfw.jpg&h=23ca46bb&s={SIZE}\" />呢班人去晒邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b465e9b35eb6c7e961fa91715fb197eee155326f","tid":1844024,"uid":58335,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T1